<head>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
<style>
    body{
        background-color: #ddd;   
    }
    h1,.content{
    margin: 0px;
    padding: 0px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;    
}
.section{
    width:100%;
    min-height: 100vh;
    
}
.container{
    width: 80%;
    display: block;
    margin: auto;
    padding-top: 30px;
    
}
.content-section{
    float:left;
    width: 55%;
    
}
.image-section{
    float: right;
    width: 40%;
   
    
}
.image-section img{
   width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    margin-top: 10px;

}
.content-section .title{
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 28px;
   

}

.content-section .content h3{
   
    color: #5d5d5d;
    margin-right: 300px;
    font-size: 19px;
}
.content-section .content p{
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    text-align: justify;
    text-justify: inter-word;

    
}
.content-section .content b{
    margin-left: 2px;
    font-size: 20px;
}
.content-section .content .button {
    margin-top: 30px;
    
}
.content-section .content .button a{
    background-color: #3d3d3d;
    padding: 12px 40px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 25px;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    margin-left: 10px;
}
.content-section .content .button a:hover{
    background-color: #a52a2a;
    color: #fff;
}
.content-section .social{
    margin-top: 40px;
    
}
.content-section .social i{
    color:#0082e6;
    font-size: 30px;
    padding: 0px 10px;
    
}
.content-section .social i:hover{
    color: #3d3d3d;
    
}
@media screen and (max-width:768px){
    .container{
    width: 80%;
    display: block;
    margin: auto;
    padding-top: 50px;
    
}
.content-section{
    float:none;
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
    margin: auto;
    
}
    .image-section{
    float:none;
    width: 100%;
    
    }
    .image-section img{
        width:100%;
        height: auto;
        display: block;
        margin: auto;
        
    }
    .content-section .title{
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 19px;
    }
    .content-section .content .button{
        text-align: center;
    }
    .content-section .content .button a{
     padding: 9px 30px;
    }
  
    .content-section .content h3{
    margin-left: 10px;
    color: #5d5d5d;
    font-weight: normal;
    
    }
    
}

</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content-section">
            <div class="title">
                 <h1>About Us</h1>
                 
            </div> 
            <div class="content">
                <b>Find Computer programming articles. Search Here Now!</b>
                <p>programming articles With Us.Programming is at the heart of open source software. Learning programming is a great way to explore new ideas and create programs that are useful for you. This year, Opensource.com authors shared many excellent articles about programming, from how new programmers can get started, to how experts can learn more about the details. Here are some articles to get you excited about programming.Programming is hard work, but it's also a lot of fun. Read up on a new library, a new language, or a new technique, and then go and put it into practice. And of course, make it open source!

                 </p>
         
               <%=link_to'Articles listing',articles_path ,class:"btn btn-secondary"%>|
               <%=link_to'Home page',root_path,class:"btn btn-secondary"%>
            </div>
  
    </div>
       <div class="image-section">
            <%= image_tag("logos/article.jpg") %>
       </div>
    </div>
</div>
    